      "writtenOn": "2019-10-04T20:04:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "it already does not mirror Build. If we wanted them to be mirrors, we\u0027d want to use Build itself.\n\nScheduleBuildRequest and Build are quite different, so i think it is ok not to couple them.\nFor example, ScheduleBuildRequest by itself is not sufficient. A builder configuration must live on the server, and together they may produce a Build.\n\nWhen we have time, I\u0027d expect this service to grow\n  rpc CreateBuild(CreateBuildRequest) Build\n\nwith\n\n  message CreateBuildRequest {\n    Build build;\n  }",
